The output of a wind turbine depends on the turbine’s size and the wind’s speed through the rotor [29]. The turbine rated power as shown in Eq. 25 was obtained
25=ActualPD×area of the rotor=43×6.8W=0.292kW\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
